title: Seeking 62
description:
Tony Kornheiser and Michael Wilbon discuss if it will put a damper on Aaron Judge’s season if he doesn’t get to 62 home runs for the season, if the Rams are diminished by their loss to the 49ers last night and if expectations are too high for Victor Wembanyama.
